OL,3,COfficer says it's 'difficult to
OL,4,Cunderstand' how Southport killer
OL,5,Cinjured so many
OL,7,FA police officer has told a public
OL,8,Finquiry into the Southport attack that
OL,9,Fhe found it "difficult to understand"
OL,10,Fhow one person could have inflicted so
OL,11,Fmany injuries.
OL,13,FChief Inspector Andrew Hughes was one
OL,14,Fof two force incident managers in the
OL,15,FMerseyside Police control room on 29
OL,16,FJuly 2024, when 999 calls came in
OL,17,Freporting "a boy with a knife" had
OL,18,Fattacked a number of young girls at
OL,19,Fthe Hart Space.
