OL,3,COfficer says it's 'difficult to
OL,4,Cunderstand' how Southport killer
OL,5,Cinjured so many
OL,7,FThe killer, referred to by his
OL,8,Finitials AR by the inquiry, murdered
OL,9,FElsie Dot Stancombe, seven, Bebe King,
OL,10,Fsix, and Alice da Silva Aguiar, nine,
OL,11,Fand attempted to murder 10 others in
OL,12,Fthe attack at the Taylor Swift-themed
OL,13,Fdance class.
OL,15,FMr Hughes said: "The amount of
OL,16,Fcasualties... I found it difficult to
OL,17,Funderstand how one person could
OL,18,Finflict that many injuries to that
OL,19,Fmany people, so a consideration for me
OL,20,Fwas that there might be more offenders
OL,21,Fthat we hadn't yet encountered."
