OL,5,Cinjured so many
OL,7,FMr Hughes went on to explain to the
OL,8,Finquiry, sitting at Liverpool Town
OL,9,FHall, the immediate response of
OL,10,FMerseyside Police in the hours after
OL,11,Fthe attack.
OL,13,FMr Hughes said that nearby unarmed
OL,14,Fofficers were deployed with
OL,15,Finstructions to deal with the
OL,16,Fsituation if was safe to do so, while
OL,17,Farmed response vehicles made their way
OL,18,Fto Southport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
