OL,5,Cinjured so many
OL,7,FThe inquiry heard Sergeant Gregory
OL,8,FGillespie and PC Luke Holden, armed
OL,9,Fwith a Taser, entered the building and
OL,10,Fdetained AR.
OL,12,FMr Hughes said armed response officers
OL,13,Fcontinued to the scene even after the
OL,14,Fsuspect was arrested.
OL,16,FThe inquiry heard AR did not give any
OL,17,Fdetails when asked who he was at the
OL,18,Fscene, so was not identified until a
OL,19,Fcall from taxi driver Gary Poland.
