OL,7,FThe log also noted: "He has been
OL,8,Flogging onto school websites which
OL,9,Finvolve school mass shootings and he
OL,10,Ftalks about guns and beheadings."
OL,12,FMr Hughes said he decided to send
OL,13,Farmed officers to carry out a search
OL,14,Fof AR's home on Old School Close in
OL,15,FBanks, Lancashire.
