OL,3,COfficer says it's 'difficult to
OL,4,Cunderstand' how Southport killer
OL,5,Cinjured so many
OL,7,FHe said: "There were a number of
OL,8,Fscenarios I was considering. There
OL,9,Fcould be other offenders, this is part
OL,10,Fof some sort of planned operation to
OL,11,Flure police in. There could be a
OL,12,Fthreat to officers when they arrive.
OL,14,F"He could have injured family members,
OL,15,Fthere could be injured people at that
OL,16,Flocation."
