OL,3,COfficer says it's 'difficult to
OL,4,Cunderstand' how Southport killer
OL,5,Cinjured so many
OL,7,FMr Hughes accepted that "perhaps" it
OL,8,Fwould have been possible for him to
OL,9,Fhave declared a major incident earlier
OL,10,Fthan 12.14pm but said he was waiting
OL,11,Ffor the number of casualties to be
OL,12,Fconfirmed.
OL,14,FHe said declaring it earlier would not
OL,15,Fhave made a difference to the number
OL,16,Fof resources available or the speed
OL,17,Fthey got there.
