OL,3,COfficer says it's 'difficult to
OL,4,Cunderstand' how Southport killer
OL,5,Cinjured so many
OL,7,FMr Hughes said he felt his training
OL,8,Fhad prepared him for dealing with the
OL,9,Fincident and he did not feel
OL,10,Foverwhelmed.
OL,12,FHe said: "It was a very chaotic,
OL,13,Fhorrific incident which gets landed on
OL,14,Fyou with no warning whatsoever but I
OL,15,Ffelt able to discharge my duties
OL,16,Feffectively."
OL,18,FThe inquiry continues.
